com.github.davidmhewitt.torrential (1.0.9) xenial; urgency=low

  * Torrential now watches your download folder for new torrent files while it's running
  * Torrent files are now moved to the trash after they have been added
  * Added a copy magnet link entry to the right click menu
  * Minor quality of life improvements and code cleanup

 -- David Hewitt <davidmhewitt@gmail.com>  Wed, 06 Jun 2018 20:57:24 +0100

